## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not cover all possible strategies for environmental protection. The effectiveness of the suggested actions can vary based on geographic, economic, and social contexts. Additionally, the report relies on secondary data, which may not reflect the most current research or innovations in environmental conservation. Further research and localized studies could provide more tailored recommendations.